				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I love this spell.  I go to south karana and kill aviaks.  I can kite yellows easily.  I just cast skin like rock and barbcoat on myself, then i pull with snare.  I dot it and run for a little.  Then i give it 2 blasts of careless lightning and run till my dot runs out.  then i recast the dot and cast shield of barbs on me.  every time i get hit it hits the thing back for 10 points of damage.  The extra 2 damage that barbcoat adds helps so much.  If u dont use this spell u will have a lot harder time lvling.  i get a blue bubble of experience a kill.  hope that helps.<BR>
